{"_id":"4JP2oQX9qZOiZv9Q","name":"Cailleach 1957","type":"weapon","img":"systems/cyberpunk-red-core/icons/compendium/weapons/veryHeavyPistol.svg","data":{"tags":[],"description":{"value":"<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">The Cailleach 1957 is a Variant Heavy Pistol and an upgrade to the Ceridwen 1903 that is concealed within a machined steel cigarette case. The case has an inset button on one side that causes internal mechanisms to infold and expand. When the weapon is in its case form it provides a +4 bonus to any checks to conceal the weapon, the case also has room for eight cigarettes, these can be accessed through the use of a second inset button.</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-8f3c598b-7fff-e247-caf6-4732e2eacfb3\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">When the case has been expanded into its weapon form it takes the same base profile as a Heavy Pistol with some small changes. This Variant Heavy Pistol has an unmodifiable magazine capacity of 4 and deals 4d6 damage. It can be reloaded with an action in either form.</span></p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Oghma's Collection","favorite":false,"price":{"market":500,"category":"expensive"},"quality":"standard","amount":1,"isUpgraded":false,"upgrades":[],"equipped":"owned","concealable":true,"isConcealed":false,"weaponType":"heavyPistol","weaponSkill":